{"title":"Impactación fecal","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/- Impactación fecal.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Impactación fecal","guid":"GBs37j8wBgqJIjgm8jPgVw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Definición ","guid":"cgLrULHCaQ9KG4e-Kb-9Kw","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Materia fecal engrosada y endurecida en el recto o el\\Ncolon no se puede evacuar espontáneamente.","guid":"gyE1L9fSpvybJpXcIkP89Q","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Se ve con mayor frecuencia en pacientes ancianos o pediátricos\\Ncomo una complicación del estreñimiento crónico.","guid":"DfPoNqKxzyf14PC0XuvjVQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"4","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"bfvUD0l5KVqRq1tkQ51YlQ","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"Puede afectar hasta al 40 % de los pacientes mayores en entornos de vida asistida o hospitalarios","guid":"I9bHnX5HH0E2LIoE37PUNA","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"4","text":"Causa frecuente de visitas al departamento de emergencias para los residentes de hogares de ancianos.","guid":"SomCHAZtO1Av_uPj5rzt1A","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"0","text":"Factores\\Nde riesgo","guid":"4Is4F0L9MDoVts2VZLPBRg","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"Inmovilidad o estado de confinamiento en la cama","guid":"S3XKXDYzoOEAq2cr5dF_lA","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"Medicamentos que causan hipomotilidad","guid":"e6NuKGtYEUA5xk8CMEaNbg","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"7","text":"Afecciones anatómicas, como fisura anal, cirugía anal pasada o enfermedad de Hirschsprung","guid":"TwdbD7crIcHUgFcJ3QVP0A","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"7","text":"Afecciones neuropsiquiátricas, como la demencia.","guid":"6OT8jyy3AvV1pHV1PSKxjg","children":[]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"0","text":"Clínica ","guid":"","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"Dolor abdominal e hinchazón","guid":"AWlGn5G6MgPIrokVJqm7Vg","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"12","text":"Dificultad para evacuar los intestinos","guid":"mTAp97JdjeI1n9J3yt2_IA","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"12","text":"Molestias rectales","guid":"hciwq_xc4nZaNsjstdvaeg","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"12","text":"Diarrea o incontinencia fecal con el paso de heces blandas\\No acuosas debido a la filtración alrededor de la masa fecal.","guid":"UJG3XsFBwTajpaO84g7IbA","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"12","text":"Ancianos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"Aumento de la confusión o la agitación","guid":"DN2QaakMcNuyb2rF3Cm60w","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"Disautonomia con inestabilidad hemodinámica","guid":"QjUHbfKgE0Dg-gaPzJA8HQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"12","text":"Puede provocar daño\\Nen pared intestinal","guid":"Eie3_ECfA9d2uGjp2iUCNA","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"Isquemia, necrosis, ulceración,\\Nperforación y peritonitis.","guid":"t7WjmRPXcYPFmMEYZciS_Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"0","text":"Estudio","guid":"mW7qPGrSRAVhfv7xp1jDOA","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"Imagenes","guid":"","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"Modalidades","guid":"","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"Radiografía abdominal","guid":"qsoUr84GLYhnBmNf8txArQ","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"Incluida la vejiga ureter renal vertical\\N(KUB)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"24","text":"Tmografía\\Ncomputarizada (TC)","guid":"p-Jb2cGAKaXn-bEOImbAUA","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"Evaluar las heces intraluminales, los signos de\\Nobstrucción y descartar una perforación si se sospecha.","guid":"8a7BpXYy500ZLzwXaf3PUA","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"24","text":"Considerar ecografía","guid":"sj25AIc9B_yeKoHlSfv-NA","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"Embarazadas y niños","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"23","text":"Signos de\\Nimpactación fecal","guid":"gjdlhGiU_KgsvG4OsfBXdg","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"Asas dilatadas intestinales con niveles de líquido de aire","guid":"VUO82AivOM9PxgYJTpiAXw","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"Fecaloma","guid":"tnFRVqbVBE8kjhJfjvSnAQ","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"Grandes masas de materia\\Nfecal en el colon o el recto","guid":"JhWrR9buwMeWNytENuQUfA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"23","text":"Signos de\\Nperforación","guid":"eEPTES2NBshhKSGMBZkjMQ","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"Aire libre debajo del diafragma en\\NRadiografía de abdomen de pie","guid":"eP7qiCehMBlk5kE_yTjmKw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico diferencial","guid":"2FZWxcIL9j8L1H6-9QSEsg","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"Otras causas de dolor abdominal\\Ninferior con o sin síntomas intestinales","guid":"KQ124lpkgfvKxEkxIurJRA","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"Apendicitis, diverticulitis,\\Ncáncer de ovario o ruptura de quiste ovárico","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"Otras posibles causas\\Nde obstrucción","guid":"-IjwTxoGR_2s022xCH5FtQ","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"Obstrucción del intestino delgado, el\\Ncáncer colorrectal o un cuerpo extraño.","guid":"6iEce611R8gt0aiulWivsQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"0","text":"Manejo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"Cirugía\\Nabdominal","guid":"9EuMs_zHVsUfw2d3_dn5sQ","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"Perforación, peritonitis o\\Nhemorragia masiva","guid":"yU_5xy2PEF6G8t09VKYICQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"42","text":"Desimpactación","guid":"5mIfK3FbmpEmSoeX1fUddQ","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"Factores a considerar para\\Nelección de método","guid":"","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"Presencia de obstrucción estructural","guid":"n9_GUI1x6onPjbnoQmM41g","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"Posicionamiento de la materia fecal\\N(ubicada proximal o distalmente)","guid":"vvKjV9ONzJ-kRklsMzVW0Q","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"46","text":"Edad","guid":"Qg4EyEmSLPbnG57lgZAVlw","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"46","text":"Estado de movilidad","guid":"lrVesgolKWYmw0thqLeuTg","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"46","text":"Riesgo de aspiración del paciente","guid":"yWnQUUrb7w_ihJV7HlvIiw","children":[]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"45","text":"Obstrucción completa y\\Nuna impactación distal","guid":"SJcoouHP2w27PZJGwMZ3FA","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"Desimpactación manual y/o un supositorio\\Nrectal o un enema para la limpieza fecal.","guid":"JV4i_iMKKeXuxBNVTKc0Dw","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"Supositorios\\Nestimulantes","guid":"TEv7XdxhGldl5DAXWpmsgA","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"Bisacodil o la glicerina","guid":"_RGocNrbCESV-8jRAvelZw","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"54","text":"Considerar antes de enema","guid":"lBEFbd9OPkjgd3y4Ntw5JQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"52","text":"Enemas","guid":"7ZlvrxGIsyj7aTXo5CZ3Bw","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"Agua tibia con sorbitol y jarabe de sodio\\Ndocusato, o enema de aceite mineral.","guid":"8STxPA2JRP1zRpgny_28Bg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"45","text":"Materia fecal localizada\\Nproximalmente sin obstrucción","guid":"4VG8Yhg_Q4ZTA_c1gsK7Pw","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"Asegurar movilidad del paciente y\\Nacceso a instalaciones de aseo","guid":"9qmCTXELNQeWAl33f9zjyw","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"59","text":"Llaxante\\Nosmótico oral","guid":"rFEQn7OhjWR5DyPDz4XmXw","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"PEG con o sin electrolitos como la\\Nopción de primera línea","guid":"IMEZCfSpimQKjHXPITUjQw","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"PEG 3350 17 g en 250 cm de agua cada 15 minutos hasta\\Nque el paciente pase las heces u 8 vasos consumidos","guid":"-T1OvHVZjc14yqyz_67Bhg","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"62","text":"PEG con electrolitos 1-2 L una\\Nvez al día durante 1-2 días","guid":"k-l3061jW9QYZIfy4q4gKw","children":[]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"61","text":"Lactulosa 15-30 ml (10-20 g de lactulosa) por\\Nvía oral una vez al día durante 24-48 horas","guid":"zmygYkLcU5glaFWDZjQA9A","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"61","text":"Citrato de magnesio 30-60 ml por vía oral con\\N100 ml de líquidos claros, cada 4-8 horas","guid":"jGKRG85K0hn1VafBmOQc_w","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"42","text":"Terapia de\\Nmantenimiento","guid":"bOEOagQ8VjSjACQFGNvEXg","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"Recurrencia es común ","guid":"whmqb1ceRivgF8lkT9TIhw","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"Evalúe las causas subyacentes y los factores de riesgo","guid":"wxflbbU3MTqMn_ni57qJxw","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"Si aún no se\\Nconocen","guid":"mL9Wsv_pP2h5kEei7Onnog","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"Aconseje la terapia de mantenimiento para el estreñimiento\\Ncrónico a menos que se identifique una causa reversible.","guid":"wnBxqWwhMtfX2a_t08D20g","children":[]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"67","text":"Opciones de terapia\\Nde mantenimiento","guid":"2w8gZNnXwR3x2OS_tBCrpw","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"PEG 17 g/día","guid":"3RI43iW0nU1jqyixEUHu5A","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"Lactulosa 10-20 g/día","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"67","text":"Impactación inducida\\Npor opioides","guid":"4lfWx56jEBZMN7yZmnfY8A","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"Terapias convencionales para el estreñimiento,\\Ncomo ablandadores de heces o agentes osmóticos","guid":"HqXs1ua3RjhAKDhtONwJQQ","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"Antagonistas de los\\Nreceptores de opioides","guid":"ytGjDKbLv8Y_mgtSToHQvQ","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"Metilnaltrexona,\\Nalvimopan o naloxona","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"75","text":"Prucaloprida","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]}]},"node_count":79,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas","filename":"- Impactación fecal","id":"map_56","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"- Impactación fecal"}